&lt;p&gt;Graham Capital Management, L.P. is seeking a highly organized and detail-oriented trading and legal documentation professional to join the firm Legal team. This individual will work closely with a small team including senior attorneys in a fast-paced legal environment covering every aspect of Graham Capital’s business. In this role, you will assist with contracts (including trading and vendor contracts), workﬂows, and databases, as well as support daily tasks related to legal operations and ad hoc projects as needed.&amp;nbsp; The ideal candidate thrives in a collaborative setting, has a strong work ethic and takes pride in their work product, and is eager to learn and become fluent with a wide range of legal documentation and verticals.&lt;/p&gt;
